Title: Charity Raffle
Book Description: Stop by the Charity Raffle table (by Ops and Registration) and purchase a raffle ticket or bid for some amazing prizes (we'll have them on display) in support of our charity- All Hands Active! Prizes winners will be announced at Closing Ceremonies- and you must be present to win.

Title: Inclusivity and Diversity in Tech
Book Description: Guest of Honor Deb Nicholson and Chioke Mose-Telesford from Grand Circus lead an open discussion to share and discuss strategies and initiatives to increase diversity and inclusivity in tech.
